<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_38_r1l18"><expan>Sebolt<ex>en</ex></expan> pfıncʒıng vnd <expan>Sıgmund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Strom<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_38_r1l19"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als ewch wol <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ıſt vvie wir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l20"><expan>Pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchrıftlıche <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l22">ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan></del> nehſt geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Der 
<add><ab facs="#facs_38_r1l21">dıener </ab></add> ıſt nu <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l23">Vnd als vıl der <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Jurıſten gelernt vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l24">der Jurıſt vns eıns teıls <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> wır <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l26">denn daʒ dem <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dıe ſache 
<add><ab facs="#facs_38_r1l25">von der Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc </ab></add> vaſt auſʒ dem ſınn <expan>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey vnd an <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l27"><expan>ſtepf<ex>an</ex></expan> ſeın <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> noch nichts gearbeytt hab . / Das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l28">daʒ Jr eẅch deſt ee ʒu <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> füget als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r1l29">Jr denn vor von vns gefertıgt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyt wan des nu bas notdurft </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_39" id="18v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_39_r1l1">ıſt als Jr ſelbs wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mugt vnd dıe ſache da in acht habt ſo Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_39_r1l3">beſt mugt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_39_r1l2">ob es ʒu <expan>gute<ex>m</ex></expan> end <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht </ab></add> / als wır nıht ʒweıfeln daʒ Jr gern tut . das ıſt vns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_39_r1l4"><expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol ʒu dank / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> marıe magdalene . <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_39_r1l5"><expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıcıuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_38" id="18r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Sebolt<ex>en</ex></expan> Pfinczing und
                            <expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Strom<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ewch wol
                            <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ist, wie wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> schriftliche <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nehst
                        gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, der <add>diener</add> ist nu
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und als vil der <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        juristen gelernt und auch der jurist uns eins teils
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, so
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> wir <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        niht, denn daz dem <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die sache <add>von der
                            juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.</add> vast ausz dem sinn
                                <expan>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> sey und an
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Stepf<ex>an</ex></expan>, sein <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan>, noch
                        nichts gearbeytt hab. Das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        ewch, daz ir ewch dest ee zu <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> füget, als ir denn vor von uns
                        gefertigt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> seyt, wan des nu bas notdurft <pb facs="#facs_39" id="18v"/>ist, als ir selbs wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>
                        mugt und die sache da in acht habt, so ir best mugt, <add>ob es zu
                                    <expan>gute<ex>m</ex></expan> end <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            möcht</add>, als wir niht zweifeln, daz ir gern tut. Das ist uns
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ewch <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        wol zu dank. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Marie Magdalene <expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan>
                        sigillo <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
